Drew Scott's Informatic 102 Webpage

Informatics 102 Portfolio

This is my Info 102 class website, where I will be keeping a compilation of (most) all the works I do in class.

![](http://i.imgur.com/VH9zxjl.jpg)

Currently I am not only working on getting the website up and running but also working on my group and I's project, which is to build an Emergency Response App into phones so that the process of coming to a person in need of help can be facilitated more efficiently.
